      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor category.",
      "rationale": "Model form uncertainty not formally quantified at MRL 2. RANS k-omega SST turbulence model selected based on prior literature for rotating machinery hemolysis prediction."
    },
