    "rationale": "The CFD model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Seven credibility factors were assessed and found to meet or exceed requirements at MRL 2. Six factors were not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 scoping. The overall evidence package supports sufficient model credibility for the intended COU.",
